  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The present study aimed to investigate the effect of exercise program on health-quality of
      life (HQL) in older adults.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The questionnaire consisted of demographic data (such as age, gender, educational level, and
      employment) and the LEIPAD questionnaire used to measure HQL.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
